graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>Job Queueing System]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|autoscaling| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Job Framework Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|ML training| KubeflowTraining[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>v1, v2beta1<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|distributed jobs| JobSetController[JobSet Controller<br/>v1alpha2<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Kueue -.->|Ray workloads| RayOperator[Ray Operator<br/>v1<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Kueue -->|CRD webhooks| KubeflowTraining
    Kueue -->|CRD webhooks| RayOperator
    Kueue -->|metrics scraping| MonitoringStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>ServiceMonitor]

    %% Integration Points (ODH Components)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| Kueue
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto-deploy jobs| Kueue
    Workbenches[Workbenches] -.->|submit jobs| Kueue

    %% Core Kubernetes APIs
    Kueue -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
    K8sAPI -->|webhook calls| Kueue

    %% Job Types Managed
    subgraph JobTypes["Job Types Supported"]
        BatchJob[Batch Job<br/>batch/v1]
        TFJob[TFJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        MPIJob[MPIJob<br/>kubeflow.org/v2beta1]
        RayJobType[RayJob/RayCluster<br/>ray.io/v1]
        JobSetType[JobSet<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io/v1alpha2]
    end

    Kueue -->|manages| BatchJob
    Kueue -->|manages| TFJob
    Kueue -->|manages| PyTorchJob
    Kueue -->|manages| MPIJob
    Kueue -->|manages| RayJobType
    Kueue -->|manages| JobSetType

    %% CRDs Provided
    subgraph KueueCRDs["Kueue CRDs (kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1)"]
        ClusterQueue[ClusterQueue<br/>Cluster quotas]
        LocalQueue[LocalQueue<br/>Namespace queues]
        Workload[Workload<br/>Job representation]
        ResourceFlavor[ResourceFlavor<br/>Resource types]
        AdmissionCheck[AdmissionCheck<br/>Policies]
        WorkloadPriority[WorkloadPriorityClass<br/>Priorities]
        ProvisioningConfig[ProvisioningRequestConfig<br/>Autoscaler]
    end

    Kueue -->|provides| ClusterQueue
    Kueue -->|provides| LocalQueue
    Kueue -->|provides| Workload
    Kueue -->|provides| ResourceFlavor
    Kueue -->|provides| AdmissionCheck
    Kueue -->|provides| WorkloadPriority
    Kueue -->|provides| ProvisioningConfig

    %% Styling
    style Kueue fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style K8s fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External Optional
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
